rComments: Derek is awesome.  I was burned out on German but he made the class a lot of fun.  If you can get him as your TA, do it.

Herr Drake is the best TA I ever had! He's very dedicated and he knows a whole lot of German. His accent is really really good and you couldn't tell that he's from America. You don't wanna be a smart-aleck in his class though...
